#\#CIF_2.0
# Tests: FK accumulator / propagation link. _diffrn_radiation.id establishes
# the parent radiation source. _diffrn_radiation_wavelength.radiation_id is not
# explicitly present in the loop; instead, the ingestion engine propagates
# the value 'Cu_tube' from the diffrn_radiation row to fill the FK column in
# every diffrn_radiation_wavelength row.
# Dictionary: cif_pow

