_diffrn_radiation.id    Cu_tube
_diffrn_radiation.probe x-ray
loop_
  _diffrn_radiation_wavelength.id
  _diffrn_radiation_wavelength.value
  _diffrn_radiation_wavelength.wt
  Ka1  1.54056  0.670
  Ka2  1.54439  0.330
